divs: Sighting Detailsnice morning,some sun.i was sitting on my front porch,it was quiet.when all of a sudden this thing flys from my right this side of post,in front of me,past me,around the outside of other post swung around and flew away to my left.i stood up.went to the rail and tried to see it going away.no way.it was clear like a jelly fish,not shiney.twisted as it flew.no sound,except slight soft hiss when flew past me.i was surprised,i seen all kinds of things,never that.iwent down the stairs to the street,and looked around hopeing to see some one else that seen it too.nope.no one around.ive asked very few about this and,well,you know,not sure what to say except i did witness this as i discribed,i swear.barry g.
